{"type": "article", "id": 23198, "title": "可移动的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-03T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 103, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133812UgmQIve1WXO6xGTw.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款可移动的灯，来自洛杉矶设计工作室 Feltmark。依靠安装在墙上的磁性支架，让它可贴在多个位置上。灯里含有太阳能电池板，所以不受插头和电线的限制，充电一天可供 6 个月的电，很适合放在走廊或卧室里成为一盏夜灯。而小巧的外形也可以让它带到旅游途中作为手电筒使用。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/byfeltmark/ellum-solar-light-different\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133809cSHjfmk6qp8b9e3n.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133810RictBsoQ5G179MIa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133810KPatXpuq7iOxm9Lf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133811YC1zHrx36seULBXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133811NB9W02c7IUuqjRrs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}